194
00:17:54,042 --> 00:17:56,110
Namun ia belum datang sama sekali.

195
00:17:56,177 --> 00:17:57,778
<i>sejak tiba
di King's Landing.</i>

196
00:17:57,812 --> 00:18:00,914
<i>aku berbaring di sini,
wajahku terbelah dua,</i>

197
00:18:00,982 --> 00:18:03,484
